          <p class="mt-5 max-w-[730px] text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-[rgba(255,255,255,0.85)] lg:text-[16px]">
            Our <strong class="font-bold text-white">Mobile</strong> and <strong class="font-bold text-white">Web Application;</strong> targeted on assisting you into the right turns of your investment management journey. We are built on a foundation to evolve as and when the market demands it.
